description:
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span&gt;Southern Health NHS Foundation Trust are looking to recruit motivated, caring and enthusiastic Nursing Associates to join the team at Alton Community Hospital...&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;Anstey ward is offering a fantastic development opportunity for a motivated, forward thinking individuals who are dedicated to providing excellent care. This is an opportunity to demonstrate your skills as a Nursing Associate who is focused on continually improving outcomes for patients. At Southern Health we are keen to ensure you use all of your skills as a Nursing Associate including medication management and developing holistic plans of care.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;With the launch of Integrated Intermediate Care, Alton Community Hospital is focusing on new initiatives and aims to prevent acute hospital admissions. With increased patient acuity this is an exciting opportunity to deliver more acute complex nursing care in the community setting.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span&gt;Anstey ward also offers rehabilitation for patients to promote independence and optimize functional ability to enable them to return to their own homes. &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;Alton Community Hospital is a short drive away from Basingstoke, Winchester and Guildford and offers free parking. There is a direct train line to London so is a perfect commuter town.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;If you have a good level of clinical skills and is ready for a new and exciting challenge to make a difference, this could be the ideal post for you.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;Informal visits are welcomed or please telephone to discuss what Anstey ward has to offer.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;We pride ourselves on flexible working and work life balance. &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt; Follow us on Facebook and on Twitter:&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
